		<title>養狗後生活差很大！從這「5大」真實改變一次看</title>
		<link>https://firenews.com.tw/2025/09/27/%e9%a4%8a%e7%8b%97%e5%be%8c%e7%94%9f%e6%b4%bb%e5%b7%ae%e5%be%88%e5%a4%a7%ef%bc%81%e5%be%9e%e9%80%99%e3%80%8c5%e5%a4%a7%e3%80%8d%e7%9c%9f%e5%af%a6%e6%94%b9%e8%ae%8a%e4%b8%80%e6%ac%a1%e7%9c%8b/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[火報 時事新聞]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Sat, 27 Sep 2025 05:01:43 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[新寵]]></category>
